description.en: The Aureus Nummus Gold (Aureus Nummus, symbol: ANG) is a gold backed fintech project that has set itself the goal of becoming the worldʼs largest non-legal tender currency; its major hallmark is its easy exchangeability into gold and fiat currencies, precious metals, precious stones as well as most other commodities.
